data.title: Gary Murray Award for Outstanding Service and Dedication to the Alabama Master Gardener Program Recipients
data.meta_description: The Gary Murray Outstanding Service and Dedication Award is presented annually and honors non-master gardeners who have contributed to the master gardener program in an outstanding way.
data.text: The Alabama Master Gardeners Association is a 501(c)(3) Nonprofit Corporation - Assisting Local Associations in Horticulture Programs for the Community
